Product Catalog Website

A simple HTML Product Catalog website that showcases products from different categories with descriptions, prices, availability, images, specifications, and links to view more details.

📌 Features

Product categories:

💻 Electronics

👕 Clothing

🏠 Home


Easy navigation using internal links

Product images

Product descriptions

Price and availability information

Product specifications

External "View Details" links

Simple and beginner-friendly HTML structure


🛠️ Technologies Used

HTML5


📂 Project Structure

Product-Catalog/
│── index.html
└── README.md

📖 Products Included

Electronics

Laptop

Mobile Phone


Clothing

T-Shirt

Jeans


Home

Table Lamp

Throw Pillows


🚀 How to Run

1. Download or clone the repository.


2. Open the project folder.


3. Double-click index.html or open it in any web browser.



🎯 Learning Concepts

This project demonstrates:

HTML document structure

Headings and paragraphs

Lists (ul, li)

Images (img)

Hyperlinks (a)

Sections (section)

IDs and page navigation

Footer

Semantic HTML


